    "description": "Modo Defense is a strategy tower defense game.<br>You can obtain various resources by spinning yut, which is similar to a dice, and use them to summon towers, strengthen towers, or use items that give additional abilities.<br>As a new mountain god, the player must learn how to use the jangseung and treasures and defend the village from ghosts.<br>Players can freely combine the treasures of Jangseung.<br>You can build towers that are single-hit or multi-attack.<br>Depending on how you combine the treasures, the difficulty can be made easier or harder.<br>You can make the game easier by clearing the map and enhancing your attributes with the stars you get.<br>Challenge yourself to see how many rounds you can last and which map you can reach!<br><br><strong> Spin the yut!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307010/extras/ab40fe40a68d788f2c8eccc3c146dc73.poster.avif?t=1678595159\" width=590 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307010/extras/ab40fe40a68d788f2c8eccc3c146dc73.webm?t=1678595159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307010/extras/ab40fe40a68d788f2c8eccc3c146dc73.mp4?t=1678595159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can get numbers by spinning yut and summon jangseung.<br>If you're lucky, you might be able to move your piece all the way.<br><br><br><strong>Combine treasures!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307010/extras/796ca98df792390e5222a23dfacf4c8c.poster.avif?t=1678595159\" width=538 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307010/extras/796ca98df792390e5222a23dfacf4c8c.webm?t=1678595159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307010/extras/796ca98df792390e5222a23dfacf4c8c.mp4?t=1678595159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Higher tier towers can contain treasure.<br>Depending on how you combine treasures, it can be additive or multiplicative.<br>Freely combine treasures!<br><br><br><strong>Various maps!</strong><br><br>There are many types of maps.<br>How far can you beat the maps that get more difficult as you go further?",
